BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:termiweb-m1@termiweb.local
DTSTAMP:20260422T003008Z
SUMMARY:M1: Repository bootstrap and docs baseline
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260406
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260407
DESCRIPTION:Added the initial repo structure\, TypeScript/Vite/server scaff
 olding\, baseline docs\, and the first environment/runtime conventions. Th
 is is the phase that created the project skeleton later milestones could a
 ctually build on.\nStart: 2026-04-06\nEnd: 2026-04-06
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:termiweb-m2@termiweb.local
DTSTAMP:20260422T003008Z
SUMMARY:M2: Shared terminal backend and session model
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260406
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260407
DESCRIPTION:Added the server-side PTY/session manager\, protocol\, auth/ses
 sion handling\, and lightweight workspace persistence. This is where insta
 nce creation\, attach/select\, close\, and shared terminal I/O became real
  code paths instead of placeholders.\nStart: 2026-04-06\nEnd: 2026-04-06
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:termiweb-m3@termiweb.local
DTSTAMP:20260422T003008Z
SUMMARY:M3: Browser UI with instances\, auth\, and mobile controls
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260406
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260407
DESCRIPTION:Added the browser client\, login flow\, instance rail\, xterm i
 ntegration\, and the first usable mobile control surface. By the end of th
 is phase\, desktop and phone clients could both attach to the same live in
 stance through the browser UI.\nStart: 2026-04-06\nEnd: 2026-04-06
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:termiweb-m4@termiweb.local
DTSTAMP:20260422T003008Z
SUMMARY:M4: Local verification and launch polish
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260407
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260408
DESCRIPTION:Added the first serious verification loop\, tightened restart/r
 econnect behavior\, and cleaned up the initial launch/run path enough for 
 real local use. This is also where the project stopped feeling like a dev-
 only prototype and started behaving like an intentional app.\nStart: 2026-
 04-07\nEnd: 2026-04-07
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:termiweb-m5@termiweb.local
DTSTAMP:20260422T003008Z
SUMMARY:M5: 0.1 release polish and rendering integrity
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260408
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260418
DESCRIPTION:This milestone contains the major UI/layout refinements\, per-i
 nstance width controls\, mobile behavior fixes\, local viewport scrolling\
 , shared terminal geometry cleanup\, and the current follow-cursor work. I
 t closed after interactive CLI rendering held up in dogfooding and the ele
 vated-only run path passed live packaged verification.\nStart: 2026-04-08\
 nEnd: 2026-04-17
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:termiweb-m6@termiweb.local
DTSTAMP:20260422T003008Z
SUMMARY:M6: Installer and first-run experience
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260412
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260414
DESCRIPTION:Added packaging\, launch scripts\, optional startup-task auto-s
 tart\, uninstall\, distribution layout\, and first-run docs for a non-dev 
 Windows install path. Verified fresh-machine setup\, before-sign-in auto-s
 tart\, uninstall cleanup\, and two-device shared session on real hardware.
 \nStart: 2026-04-12\nEnd: 2026-04-13
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:termiweb-m7@termiweb.local
DTSTAMP:20260422T003008Z
SUMMARY:M7: 0.1 release and GitHub Pages download website
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260419
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260426
DESCRIPTION:This milestone should produce the tagged `0.1` release artifact
 s plus the GitHub Pages download site that points to them. The code/doc wo
 rk here is release packaging\, distribution metadata\, the website content
  that turns the build into an actual downloadable release\, and a small am
 ount of private release-support publishing that stays outside the public l
 aunch surface.\nStart: 2026-04-19\nTarget end: 2026-04-25
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:termiweb-m8@termiweb.local
DTSTAMP:20260422T003008Z
SUMMARY:M8: Marketing for an open-source\, free-to-use product
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260426
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260524
DESCRIPTION:This milestone is the full marketing phase around the product\,
  not just a bundle of launch materials. It includes messaging\, positionin
 g\, outreach\, demos\, screenshots\, announcements\, and the practical wor
 k of getting attention on a shipped open-source product.\nStart: 2026-04-2
 6\nTarget end: 2026-05-23
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
